#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:2
msgid "域名信息"
msgstr "Domain Information"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:5
msgid "Whois"
msgstr "WHOIS"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:6
msgid ""
"`Whois <https://www.whois.com/>`_ "
"可以查询域名是否被注册，以及注册域名的详细信息的数据库，其中可能会存在一些有用的信息，例如域名所有人、域名注册商、邮箱等。"
msgstr ""
"`WHOIS <https://www.whois.com/>`_ can be used to check whether a domain has "
"been registered and to query detailed registration data. The results may "
"contain useful information such as the domain owner, registrar, and email "
"addresses."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:9
msgid "搜索引擎搜索"
msgstr "Search Engine Queries"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:10
msgid "搜索引擎通常会记录域名信息，可以通过 ``site: domain`` 的语法来查询。"
msgstr ""
"Search engines often index domain information. You can query it with syntax "
"such as ``site: domain``."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:13
msgid "第三方查询"
msgstr "Third-party Queries"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:14
msgid "网络中有相当多的第三方应用提供了子域的查询功能，下面有一些例子，更多的网站可以在 8.1 工具列表 中查找。"
msgstr ""
"Many third-party services provide subdomain lookup features. Some examples "
"are listed below; more sites can be found in the tools list in section 8.1."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:16
msgid "`DNSDumpster <https://dnsdumpster.com/>`_"
msgstr "`DNSDumpster <https://dnsdumpster.com/>`_"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:17
msgid "`Virustotal <https://www.virustotal.com/>`_"
msgstr "`VirusTotal <https://www.virustotal.com/>`_"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:18
msgid "CrtSearch"
msgstr "CrtSearch"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:19
msgid "threatminer"
msgstr "ThreatMiner"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:20
msgid "Censys"
msgstr "Censys"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:23
msgid "ASN信息关联"
msgstr "ASN Information Correlation"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:24
msgid ""
"在网络中一个自治系统 (Autonomous System, AS) "
"是一个有权自主地决定在本系统中应采用何种路由协议的小型单位。这个网络单位可以是一个简单的网络也可以是一个由一个或多个普通的网络管理员来控制的网络群体，它是一个单独的可管理的网络单元"
" (例如一所大学，一个企业或者一个公司个体) 。"
msgstr ""
"On the Internet, an Autonomous System (AS) is a network unit that has the "
"authority to decide which routing protocol to use within its own system. This"
" unit may be a simple network or a group of networks managed by one or more "
"network administrators. It is an independently manageable network unit, such "
"as a university, an enterprise, or a company."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:26
msgid ""
"一个自治系统有时也被称为是一个路由选择域 (routing domain) "
"。一个自治系统将会分配一个全局的唯一的16位号码，这个号码被称为自治系统号 (ASN) 。因此可以通过ASN号来查找可能相关的IP，例如："
msgstr ""
"An Autonomous System is sometimes also called a routing domain. Each "
"Autonomous System is assigned a globally unique 16-bit number called an "
"Autonomous System Number (ASN). Therefore, the ASN can be used to look up "
"potentially related IP addresses, for example:"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:34
msgid "域名相关性"
msgstr "Domain Correlation"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:35
msgid "同一个企业/个人注册的多个域名通常具有一定的相关性，例如使用了同一个邮箱来注册、使用了同一个备案、同一个负责人来注册等，可以使用这种方式来查找关联的域名。一种操作步骤如下："
msgstr ""
"Multiple domains registered by the same organization or individual are often "
"correlated, for example through the same registration email address, the same "
"ICP filing, or the same responsible person. These relationships can be used "
"to discover related domains. One workflow is as follows:"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:37
msgid "查询域名注册邮箱"
msgstr "Query the domain registration email address"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:38
msgid "通过域名查询备案号"
msgstr "Query the ICP filing number by domain"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:39
msgid "通过备案号查询域名"
msgstr "Query domains by ICP filing number"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:40
msgid "反查注册邮箱"
msgstr "Reverse lookup the registration email address"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:41
msgid "反查注册人"
msgstr "Reverse lookup the registrant"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:42
msgid "通过注册人查询到的域名在查询邮箱"
msgstr "Query the email addresses for domains found through the registrant"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:43
msgid "通过上一步邮箱去查询域名"
msgstr "Use the email addresses from the previous step to query domains"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:44
msgid "查询以上获取出的域名的子域名"
msgstr "Enumerate subdomains for the domains found above"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:46
msgid ""
"此外，部分公司在注册域名时，会注册不同 tld 的域名，例如 example.com / example.cn 。但是不同 tld "
"的域名也可能是由其它人注册的，需要另外辨别。"
msgstr ""
"In addition, some companies register domains under different TLDs, such as "
"example.com and example.cn. However, domains under different TLDs may also "
"have been registered by other parties, so they need to be verified "
"separately."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:50
msgid "网站信息利用"
msgstr "Using Website Information"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:51
msgid "网站中有相当多的信息，网站本身、各项安全策略、设置等都可能暴露出一些信息。"
msgstr ""
"Websites contain a large amount of information. The site itself, its security"
" policies, and its configuration may all expose useful details."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:53
msgid "网站本身的交互通常不囿于单个域名，会和其他子域交互。对于这种情况，可以通过爬取网站，收集站点中的其他子域信息。这些信息通常出现在JavaScript文件、资源文件链接等位置。"
msgstr ""
"Website interactions are usually not limited to a single domain and may "
"involve other subdomains. In this case, crawl the site to collect other "
"subdomain information. These details often appear in JavaScript files, "
"resource links, and similar locations."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:55
msgid "网站的安全策略如跨域策略、CSP规则等通常也包含相关域名的信息。有时候多个域名为了方便会使用同一个SSL/TLS证书，因此有时可通过证书来获取相关域名信息。"
msgstr ""
"Website security policies, such as cross-origin policies and CSP rules, often"
" include related domain information. Sometimes multiple domains share the "
"same SSL/TLS certificate for convenience, so certificates can also reveal "
"related domain names."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:58
msgid "HTTPS证书"
msgstr "HTTPS Certificates"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:61
msgid "证书透明度"
msgstr "Certificate Transparency"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:62
msgid "为了保证HTTPS证书不会被误发或伪造，CA会将证书记录到可公开验证、不可篡改且只能附加内容的日志中，任何感兴趣的相关方都可以查看由授权中心签发的所有证书。因此可以通过查询已授权证书的方式来获得相关域名。"
msgstr ""
"To prevent HTTPS certificates from being misissued or forged, CAs record "
"certificates in publicly verifiable, append-only, tamper-resistant logs. Any "
"interested party can review certificates issued by a certificate authority. "
"As a result, querying issued certificates can reveal related domains."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:65
msgid "SAN"
msgstr "SAN"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:66
msgid ""
"主题备用名称 (Subject Alternate Name, "
"SAN)，简单来说，在需要多个域名，并将其用于各项服务时，多使用SAN证书。SAN允许在安全证书中使用subjectAltName字段将多种值与证书关联，这些值被称为主题备用名称。"
msgstr ""
"Subject Alternative Name (SAN) certificates are commonly used when multiple "
"domain names need to be used across services. SAN allows a certificate to "
"associate multiple values through the subjectAltName field. These values are "
"called subject alternative names."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:69
msgid "域传送漏洞"
msgstr "Zone Transfer Vulnerability"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:70
msgid ""
"DNS域传送 (zone transfer) 指的是冗余备份服务器使用来自主服务器的数据刷新自己的域 (zone) "
"数据库。这是为了防止主服务器因意外不可用时影响到整个域名的解析。"
msgstr ""
"DNS zone transfer is the process in which a redundant backup server refreshes"
" its zone database using data from the primary server. This is intended to "
"prevent the entire domain's resolution from being affected if the primary "
"server unexpectedly becomes unavailable."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:72
msgid "一般来说，域传送操作应该只允许可信的备用DNS服务器发起，但是如果错误配置了授权，那么任意用户都可以获得整个DNS服务器的域名信息。这种错误授权被称作是DNS域传送漏洞。"
msgstr ""
"In general, zone transfers should only be allowed from trusted secondary DNS "
"servers. If authorization is misconfigured, any user may obtain domain "
"information for the entire DNS server. This misconfiguration is known as a "
"DNS zone transfer vulnerability."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:75
msgid "Passive DNS"
msgstr "Passive DNS"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:76
msgid ""
"Passive DNS被动的从递归域名服务器记录来自不同域名服务器的响应，形成数据库。利用Passive "
"DNS数据库可以知道域名曾绑定过哪些IP，IP曾关联到哪些域名，域名最早/最近出现的时间，为测试提供较大的帮助。Virustotal、passivetotal、CIRCL等网站都提供了Passive"
" DNS数据库的查询。"
msgstr ""
"Passive DNS passively records responses from different authoritative DNS "
"servers through recursive DNS servers and builds them into a database. A "
"Passive DNS database can show which IP addresses a domain has resolved to, "
"which domains an IP address has been associated with, and when a domain first"
" or most recently appeared. This is very helpful for testing. VirusTotal, "
"PassiveTotal, CIRCL, and similar sites provide Passive DNS database queries."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:79
msgid "泛解析"
msgstr "Wildcard DNS"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:80
msgid "泛解析是把 `*.example.com` 的所有A记录都解析到某个IP 地址上，在子域名枚举时需要处理这种情况以防生成大量无效的记录。"
msgstr ""
"Wildcard DNS resolves all A records under `*.example.com` to a specific IP "
"address. Subdomain enumeration needs to handle this case to avoid generating "
"a large number of invalid records."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:83
msgid "重要记录"
msgstr "Important Records"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:86
msgid "CNAME"
msgstr "CNAME"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:87
msgid ""
"CNAME即Canonical "
"name，又称alias，将域名指向另一个域名。其中可能包含其他关联业务的信息。很多网站使用的CDN加速功能利用了该记录。"
msgstr ""
"CNAME stands for Canonical Name and is also known as an alias. It points one "
"domain name to another domain name and may contain information about related "
"business services. Many CDN acceleration features used by websites rely on "
"this record."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:90
msgid "MX记录"
msgstr "MX Records"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:91
msgid "MX记录即Mail Exchanger，记录了发送电子邮件时域名对应的服务器地址。可以用来寻找SMTP服务器信息。"
msgstr ""
"An MX record, or Mail Exchanger record, records the server address "
"corresponding to a domain when email is sent. It can be used to identify SMTP"
" server information."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:94
msgid "NS记录"
msgstr "NS Records"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:95
msgid "NS (Name Server) 记录是域名服务器的记录，用来指定域名由哪个DNS服务器来进行解析。"
msgstr ""
"An NS (Name Server) record specifies which DNS server is responsible for "
"resolving a domain."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:98
msgid "SPF记录"
msgstr "SPF Records"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:99
msgid ""
"SPF (Sender Policy Framework) "
"是为了防止垃圾邮件而提出来的一种DNS记录类型，是一种TXT类型的记录，用于登记某个域名拥有的用来外发邮件的所有IP地址。通过SPF记录可以获取相关的IP信息，常用命令为"
" ``dig example.com txt`` 。"
msgstr ""
"SPF (Sender Policy Framework) is a DNS record type proposed to prevent spam. "
"It is a TXT record used to register all IP addresses that a domain is allowed"
" to use for outbound email. SPF records can expose related IP information. A "
"common command is ``dig example.com txt``."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:102
msgid "CDN"
msgstr "CDN"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:105
msgid "CDN验证"
msgstr "CDN Verification"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:106
msgid ""
"可通过多地ping的方式确定目标是否使用了CDN，常用的网站有 ``http://ping.chinaz.com/`` "
"``https://asm.ca.com/en/ping.php`` 等。"
msgstr ""
"You can determine whether a target uses a CDN by pinging it from multiple "
"locations. Common sites include ``http://ping.chinaz.com/`` and "
"``https://asm.ca.com/en/ping.php``."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:109
msgid "域名查找"
msgstr "Domain Lookup"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:110
msgid "使用了CDN的域名的父域或者子域名不一定使用了CDN，可以通过这种方式去查找对应的IP。"
msgstr ""
"The parent domain or subdomains of a domain using a CDN may not use the CDN. "
"This can be used to look for the corresponding IP address."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:113
msgid "历史记录查找"
msgstr "Historical Record Lookup"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:114
msgid "CDN可能是在网站上线一段时间后才上线的，可以通过查找域名解析记录的方式去查找真实IP。"
msgstr ""
"A CDN may have been enabled only after the website had been online for some "
"time. Historical DNS resolution records can therefore be used to look for the"
" real IP address."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:117
msgid "邮件信息"
msgstr "Email Information"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:118
msgid "通过社会工程学的方式进行邮件沟通，从邮件头中获取IP地址，IP地址可能是网站的真实IP或者是目标的出口IP。"
msgstr ""
"Email communication through social engineering may expose IP addresses in "
"email headers. These addresses may be the website's real IP address or the "
"target's egress IP address."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:121
msgid "子域爆破"
msgstr "Subdomain Brute Forcing"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:122
msgid "在内网等不易用到以上技巧的环境，或者想监测新域名上线时，可以通过批量尝试的方式，找到有效的域名。"
msgstr ""
"In environments such as internal networks where the above techniques are hard"
" to use, or when monitoring for newly launched domains, batch probing can be "
"used to find valid domains."

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:125
msgid "缓存探测技术"
msgstr "Cache Snooping"

#: ../../source/info/domain.rst:126
msgid ""
"在企业网络中通常都会配置DNS服务器为网络内的主机提供域名解析服务。域名缓存侦测（DNS Cache "
"Snooping）技术就是向这些服务器发送域名解析请求，但并不要求使用递归模式，用于探测是否请求过某个域名。这种方式可以用来探测是否使用了某些软件，尤其是安全软件。"
msgstr ""
"Enterprise networks usually configure DNS servers to provide name resolution "
"for internal hosts. DNS Cache Snooping sends DNS queries to these servers "
"without requiring recursive resolution, in order to detect whether a domain "
"has been requested. This method can be used to infer whether certain "
"software, especially security software, is in use."
